Author: DeFund Project
Title: DeFund Project Announcement | Pre-Sale and Crowdsale Information
Body: DeFund is a brand-new project that intends to create the first decentralized investment fund in the cryptocurrency environment!  Some information about our Token Distribution:  -- The Pre-Sale will take place from 07.16.2016 to 07.31.2018 with a price of 53,000 XDF per 1 ETH.     There will be a minimum buy of 2,650 XDF (0.05 ETH) and the distribution of 100,000,000 XDF.  -- The Crowdsale will take place from 08.07.2018 to 09.06.2018 with a price of 38,000 XDF per 1 ETH.     There will be a minimum buy of 1,900 XDF (0.05 ETH) and the distribution of 350,000,000 XDF  -- The team will withhold 50,000,000 XDF (10% of the total supply)  Get in touch with our project, Visit https://www.defundproject.net !
